I have over 15 years in the building trade including electrical  and mechanical systems, carpentry, roofing, siding, and landscaping.  I can help with your renovation needs.  Reasonable rates and free estimates.

I'm also a certified home inspector with InterNachi.  Let me ensure your home buying experience is a positive one.
